154
00:09:18,608 --> 00:09:19,328
No, you're not.

155
00:09:19,328 --> 00:09:21,007
This is the famous Shengshengman.

156
00:09:22,527 --> 00:09:24,927
Hello, may I take a photo with you?

157
00:09:25,208 --> 00:09:26,927
- No problem at all.
- Come on.

158
00:09:27,927 --> 00:09:28,568
