a Valentine's Day set meal?

202
00:11:16,728 --> 00:11:18,248
(Love at first sight)
It is popular today.

203
00:11:22,328 --> 00:11:24,208
(Love at first sight)
Then we'll have this one. Thanks.

204
00:11:24,568 --> 00:11:25,527
Okay. Wait a moment.

205
00:11:31,647 --> 00:11:34,167
