228
00:13:24,647 --> 00:13:26,968
(Should I say
I need to go back to school first?)

229
00:13:27,407 --> 00:13:28,807
(So as not to delay his work.)

230
00:13:31,527 --> 00:13:32,208
Cheng.

231
00:13:33,927 --> 00:13:34,488
Uncle.

232
00:13:35,927 --> 00:13:38,248
